{"tid":1452284,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔該咪再叫人散水，咪再話影響民意","createTime":"2019-08-12T00:41:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T02:55:35.000Z","uid":273272,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b169ae1d53934fd78f4e31c2a24f1a2bc0436930","tid":1452284,"uid":273272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T00:41:37.000Z","msg":"你哋覺得仲有得散，仲有得退咩？<br />\n<br />\n上去前面睇吓用酒嘅時候，街上途人嘅歡呼聲先啦。<br />\n<br />\n唔好話塞鐵，塞機場阻到人啦，你要我哋再有幾多人上街好似噚晚咁俾班黑警打到終身殘廢？<br />\n<br />\n塞爆個離境大堂，癱瘓個機場啦，政府就會收皮。咪再今天我，咪再大台思維，你對唔對得住天地良心。<br />\n<br />\n血海深仇。"},{"pid":"42f22fa868cf0c838b677f8cd01abef6be0350db","tid":1452284,"uid":273272,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T00:42:28.000Z","msg":"冇心機推，我只有仇恨。"},{"pid":"17376535cede2014667193841fc1c48c5715b693","tid":1452284,"uid":82175,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T00:53:25.000Z","msg":"血債血償 以眼還眼"},{"pid":"9bdd0e1631f8aa8e2a524cc02ce51965a52ad11d","tid":1452284,"uid":273272,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T00:55:41.000Z","msg":"好呀，咁都有負評。"},{"pid":"132e9181b1e2cf5cdc8db150fb60398019fa525b","tid":1452284,"uid":273272,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:39:11.000Z","msg":"好呀，係咪泛民打手入嚟負評呀。<br />\n<br />\n我哋手足隻眼點呀。<br />\n<br />\n負評講嘢呀，屌你老母。<br />\n<br />\n血海深仇。"},{"pid":"c43f76c9ad7abeea40efe0f8cee2778fc9ee8da0","tid":1452284,"uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:39:52.000Z","msg":"前線用酒果班有機會係警賊"},{"pid":"20d80374d42cf97a5f4bd938dd277c86c7432c5c","tid":1452284,"uid":273272,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c43f76c9ad7abeea40efe0f8cee2778fc9ee8da0","tid":1452284,"uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:39:52.000Z","msg":"前線用酒果班有機會係警賊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:55:35.000Z","msg":"係，但我只係想講，市民同途人唔係一面倒反對，即係所謂民意嘅嘢，唔好用嚟綑綁自己。"}]}